    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-sm-12 col-lg-12">
            <div class="alert alert-danger alert-dismissible fade show p-3" role="alert">
                Please note <strong class="monthlyRent">Rs. 8000 /-</strong> is the Rent for every <strong>Month</strong>.
                <strong class="duedateMonthly"></strong><sup>th</sup> of every <strong>Month</strong> is Due Date to pay the Rent.
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-sm-12 col-lg-12">
            <div class="alert alert-danger alert-dismissible fade show p-3" role="alert">
